      "description": "Available is a well-sorted C6 Corvette Z06, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the LS7 7.0L V8, featuring a dry-sump lubrication system and titanium connecting rods for high-RPM durability. This power is managed by a Tremec TR6060 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip rear differential. The lightweight hydroformed aluminum chassis provides exceptional torsional rigidity, paired with a performance-tuned suspension and cross-drilled ventilated rotors for superior thermal management during spirited driving. This example has been meticulously maintained, with recent attention to the valvetrain and cooling systems, ensuring the mechanical components operate at peak efficiency. While the aesthetics show honest character from road use, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive.",
